leadership_approach|people_process_results_vision|paired|people|process|results|vision|People first, Process next|You lead by building trust, confidence, and shared understanding, then turning intent into structure, sequence, and repeatable standards. This pattern is strongest when trust, communication, and shared understanding stay in view and structure, sequence, and repeatable standards support the work.|Because this is a paired pattern, People and Process work closely together. Results and Vision add range when the situation needs clearer outcomes or longer-range direction.|Build shared understanding, trust, and confidence around the work.|Process turns the approach into structure, sequence, and repeatable standards.|Results extends the approach by making progress, ownership, and next steps visible.|Vision helps you add future direction when the immediate task needs wider context.|active|leadership_approach::people_process_results_vision::paired
leadership_approach|people_process_results_vision|graduated|people|process|results|vision|People first, Process next|You lead by building trust, confidence, and shared understanding, then turning intent into structure, sequence, and repeatable standards. This pattern is strongest when trust, communication, and shared understanding stay in view and structure, sequence, and repeatable standards support the work.|Because this is a graduated pattern, the signals step down in a clear order. Start with People, use Process to strengthen the approach, then draw on Results and Vision as the situation broadens.|Build shared understanding, trust, and confidence around the work.|Process turns the approach into structure, sequence, and repeatable standards.|Results extends the approach by making progress, ownership, and next steps visible.|Vision helps you add future direction when the immediate task needs wider context.|active|leadership_approach::people_process_results_vision::graduated
